name: unbzip2-stream

scripts.prepare: mkdir dist && browserify -s unbzip2Stream index.js | uglifyjs >> dist/unbzip2-stream.min.js
scripts.prepare-long-test: dd if=/dev/urandom of=test/fixtures/vmlinux.bin bs=50x1024x1024 count=2 && cat test/fixtures/vmlinux.bin | bzip2 > test/fixtures/vmlinux.bin.bz2
